a_keys
[TITLE]The Manual:  Adventure Mode Key Bindings[/TITLE]
Here are the keys you can use to control your adventurer.
[B]
[C:7:0:1]Main Keys:[C:7:0:0]
[B]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN]
[IKEY:CURSOR_LEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_RIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP_Z]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN_Z] - Move.[R]
[IKEY:A_SAMESQUARE] - Move in own square.[R]
[IKEY:A_WAIT] - Wait for a step.[R]
[B]
[IKEY:LEAVESCREEN] - Advance/clear messages.[R]
[B]
[IKEY:A_ANNOUNCEMENTS] - View announcements.[R]
[IKEY:A_COMBAT] - Combat preferences.[R]
[IKEY:A_INV_DROP] - Drop an item.[R]
[IKEY:A_INV_EATDRINK] - Eat or drink something.[R]
[IKEY:A_GROUND] - Pickup an item.[R]
[IKEY:A_SHOOT] - Fire a projectile.[R]
[IKEY:A_INV_LOOK] - Inventory.[R]
[IKEY:A_LOOK] - Look around.[R]
[IKEY:A_TALK] - Talk to somebody.[R]
[IKEY:A_INV_PUTIN] - Put an item in a container.[R]
[IKEY:A_INV_REMOVE] - Remove an item you are wearing or from a container.[R]
[IKEY:A_STANCE] - Stand or lie down.[R]
[IKEY:A_THROW] - Throw an item.[R]
[IKEY:A_BUILDING] - Interact with a building, furniture or mechanism.[R]
[IKEY:A_INV_WEAR] - Wear an item.[R]
[IKEY:A_STATUS] - Status.[R]
[B]
[IKEY:A_ATTACK] - Attack an adjacent creature.  Change mode to wrestle.[R]
[IKEY:A_CENTER] - Center screen on yourself.[R]
[IKEY:A_DATE] - Date/time.[R]
[IKEY:A_INTERACT] - Interact with an object in an advanced way.[R]
[IKEY:A_SEARCH] - Search the nearby area very carefully.[R]
[IKEY:A_TEMPERATURE] - Temperature.[R]
[IKEY:A_LOG] - Adventure log (tasks, map, etc.).[R]
[IKEY:A_SNEAK] - Sneak.[R]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL] - Travel.[R]
[IKEY:A_WEATHER] - Weather.[R]
[IKEY:A_SLEEP] - Sleep.[R]
[B]
[C:7:0:1]Travel Keys:[C:7:0:0]
[B]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN]
[IKEY:CURSOR_LEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_RIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNRIGHT] - Move.[R]
[IKEY:A_END_TRAVEL] - Visit location.[R]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_CLOUDS] - Start/stop cloud viewing.[R]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_LOG] - Adventure log.[R]
